Well,same as you, except
we actually have a chance

103
00:06:05,820 --> 00:06:07,220
Pandora's box

104
00:06:07,610 --> 00:06:11,440
It could trap Pan for eternity
simply by opening the lid

105
00:06:12,320 --> 00:06:14,700
- You didn't tell me my father was with her.
- I didn't know

106
