116
00:06:42,060 --> 00:06:43,620
You left before we even made shore

117
00:06:44,770 --> 00:06:47,730
- You wanted to get to Henry first.
- To be on his own

118
00:06:48,180 --> 00:06:51,510
So no one could stop
you... So you can kill him

119
00:06:51,840 --> 00:06:56,500
