130
00:07:49,180 --> 00:07:54,630
This bean... can open a portal,
take you far away from this land

131
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:55,930
Even this realm

132
00:07:56,640 --> 00:07:57,950
You could start a new life

133
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:00,650
