134
00:08:01,280 --> 00:08:04,400
But he's coming back for
me as soon as he gets a job

135
00:08:04,590 --> 00:08:09,450
- The truth is,he's at the pub.He doesn't want a job.
- Or real responsibility

136
00:08:09,470 --> 00:08:13,460
Family can be a strength,but
it can also be a burden

137
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:17,830
