Because that sounds just like you

142
00:08:30,270 --> 00:08:31,550
Without me,you will fail

143
00:08:32,690 --> 00:08:34,380
I'm the most powerful amongst us

144
00:08:34,610 --> 00:08:35,860
That's why we can't trust you

145
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:38,540
If I could give you my
dagger,I would But I can't

146
00:08:38,890 --> 00:08:40,920
