181
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:20,040
Think,think,think,think,think

182
00:11:23,240 --> 00:11:25,240
Think lovely thoughts

183
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:28,280
- That's it.
- What

184
00:11:28,790 --> 00:11:31,820
When I was a boy, my father
sold me to a blacksmith

185
00:11:32,230 --> 00:11:35,110
All day in front of hot
coals,the sweat and the grime

186
00:11:35,450 --> 00:11:39,480
But every night I would say to
myself, "think lovely thoughts"

187
00:11:40,110 --> 00:11:42,950
And in my sleep,I would travel
to the most wonderful place

188
00:11:43,540 --> 00:11:48,870
- What was it called?
- Neverland

189
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:51,440
Then that's where we should go

190
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:07,590
I don't even know if this place is real

191
