We need to talk

192
00:12:31,890 --> 00:12:35,230
I've found when a woman says that,
I'm rarely in for pleasant conversation

193
00:12:35,690 --> 00:12:37,740
There has to be a way for
David to leave the island

194
00:12:38,060 --> 00:12:38,900
Well,there isn't

195
00:12:39,740 --> 00:12:41,510
He told me about your
brother,what happened

196
00:12:41,690 --> 00:12:43,740
I know it can't be easy to talk
about,but... Well,then let's not,shall we

197
00:12:43,990 --> 00:12:47,050
