an elixir back in my shop

216
00:13:34,280 --> 00:13:35,220
what is your price?

217
00:13:35,500 --> 00:13:37,760
Well,this is quite the favor

218
00:13:38,930 --> 00:13:44,760
- I'd expect one of equal weight in return.
- No

219
00:13:46,090 --> 00:13:48,340
When we get back to Storybrooke,
you're gonna save David

220
00:13:48,500 --> 00:13:49,630
because it's the right thing to do

221
00:13:49,770 --> 00:13:52,150
No deals,no favors,understand

222
00:13:55,020 --> 00:13:55,730
Fine

223
00:13:56,540 --> 00:13:57,610
I'll do as you ask

224
00:13:58,960 --> 00:14:00,660
I'll go tell David

225
00:14:08,300 --> 00:14:09,040
We're here

226
00:14:09,530 --> 00:14:10,530
Pan's perimeter

227
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:11,890
It's time

228
00:14:12,310 --> 00:14:13,750
Tink will sneak us in
the back like we planned

229
00:14:13,770 --> 00:14:15,660
We grab Henry.In and out,simple

230
00:14:16,720 --> 00:14:17,700
You good with Pan patrol

231
