234
00:14:25,860 --> 00:14:28,530
But I'm not walking in there
with nothing but my good looks

235
00:14:28,730 --> 00:14:31,920
Now I,on the other hand... Here,in
case your good looks fail you

236
00:14:32,490 --> 00:14:33,560
Thanks,mate

237
00:14:35,050 --> 00:14:35,970
Let's get Henry

238
