- No.
- I'll do it

240
00:14:54,330 --> 00:14:55,450
You remember the spell

241
00:15:12,780 --> 00:15:14,040
- Where's Pan?
- I don't know

242
00:15:16,550 --> 00:15:18,530
- Henry - He's gotta
be somewhere - Where

243
00:15:20,060 --> 00:15:20,790
Help

244
00:15:30,810 --> 00:15:32,480
You're an... an adult

245
00:15:32,970 --> 00:15:34,660
My name's Emma.I'm looking for my son

246
00:15:38,760 --> 00:15:42,040
- Wendy
- Do I know you.It's Baelfire

247
00:15:42,210 --> 00:15:46,090
- You two know each other
- Bae. - Yeah Yeah,we do

248
00:15:46,350 --> 00:15:47,310
Can it really be you

249
00:15:53,430 --> 00:15:54,760
I thought I'd never see you again

250
00:15:55,520 --> 00:15:56,930
What are you... wh...
what are you doing here

251
00:15:57,320 --> 00:15:59,210
Well,I... I came back to save you

252
00:16:00,550 --> 00:16:01,560
You did that for me

253
00:16:02,380 --> 00:16:04,950
Well,I couldn't bear for
you to be without a family,

254
00:16:05,230 --> 00:16:07,950
not after you told us that your
mother and father were both dead

255
00:16:08,220 --> 00:16:09,500
